<div class="section-container">
    <section>
        <div class="intro">
            <h1>SkylightId</h1>
            <p>
                Developed a web application using Angular, .NET, and MySQL to assist contractors in identifying and accurately measuring skylights.
                The platform streamlines the process by providing detailed measurement guidelines and skylight classification,
                reducing common inquiries and improving efficiency.
            </p>
            <a href="https://github.com/jaypowellcs" aria-label="Github"><i class="fab fa-github"></i>Github Link</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="tech">
        <h2>Technologies Used</h2>
