            <img class="image-placeholder" src="/Images/skylightidnet.png" alt="Main page of Skylight ID">
        </div>
        <div>
            <p><strong>Skylight Curb-Mounted Calculator</strong></p>
            <img class="image-placeholder" src="/Images/curbmount.png" alt="Section of the website Skylight ID">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <div class="features">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Skylight Calculator – Calculates three skylight types.</li>
                <li>Skylight Identification Tool</li>
                <li>Step-by-step measuring guide</li>
                <li>Common skylight sizes reference</li>
                <li>Contact & Support Page</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <div class="improvements">
            <h2>Room for Improvement</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>🚀 Need to host the website, still considering costs.</li>
